<subSubSection id="C337DD88FFFBFFEB3CC8FDE3FDC7BBA9" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" type="description">
<paragraph id="8B928E03FFFBFFEB3CC8FDE3FB38BB4D" blockId="4.[151,1436,1590,2013]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55">
<emphasis id="B9595211FFFBFFEB3CC8FDE3FEFEBADE" bold="true" box="[199,345,1737,1762]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55">Description.</emphasis>
Body length 
<quantity id="4CD523E6FFFBFFEB3DFDFDE3FDFEBADD" box="[498,601,1737,1761]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.39" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" unit="mm" value="1.39">1.39 mm</quantity>
, maximum width of elytra 
<quantity id="4CD523E6FFFBFFEB3F80FDE3FC50BADD" box="[911,1015,1737,1761]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.8999999999999995" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" unit="mm" value="0.59">0.59 mm</quantity>
, whole body, except posterior part of head, shiny, reddish brown, posterior part of head matt, legs and antennae yellowish brown. Head 
<number id="3DE59C24FFFBFFEB390BFDC7FA92BB39" box="[1284,1333,1773,1797]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" value="1.15">1.15</number>
times as long as wide, terminal antennomere about 
<number id="3DE59C24FFFBFFEB3E60FC3BFD35BB15" box="[623,658,1809,1833]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" value="1.5">1.5</number>
times as long as wide, with dense, long setae. Pronotum 
<number id="3DE59C24FFFBFFEB3905FC3BFA9CBB15" box="[1290,1339,1809,1833]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" value="1.33">1.33</number>
times as long as head and about 
<number id="3DE59C24FFFBFFEB3DADFC1FFE74BB71" box="[418,467,1845,1869]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" value="1.65">1.65</number>
times as wide as long. Elytra about 
<number id="3DE59C24FFFBFFEB3F60FC1FFC07BB71" box="[879,928,1845,1869]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" value="1.25">1.25</number>
times as long as abdomen, composite tergite (IV–VI) 
<number id="3DE59C24FFFBFFEB3CF5FC73FEBABB4D" box="[250,285,1881,1905]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" value="5.4">5.4</number>
times as long as tergites VII–VIII together, tergite VIII slightly longer than VII.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B928E03FFFBFFEB3CC8FC57FDC7BBA9" blockId="4.[151,1436,1590,2013]" box="[199,608,1917,1941]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55">Sexual dimorphism. Male unknown.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C337DD88FFFBFFEB3CC8FC8BFEE8BBE1" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8B928E03FFFBFFEB3CC8FC8BFEE8BBE1" blockId="4.[151,1436,1590,2013]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55">
<emphasis id="B9595211FFFBFFEB3CC8FC8BFEC7BB86" bold="true" box="[199,352,1953,1978]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55">Distribution.</emphasis>
Known only from the 
<typeStatus id="549630A1FFFBFFEB3E66FC88FD3EBB86" box="[617,665,1954,1978]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55">type</typeStatus>
locality, Danum Valley Forest Center, Ulu Segama Forest Reserve, Borneo (Sabah).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
